articles.title: A computationally designed antigen eliciting broad humoral responses against SARS-CoV-2 and related sarbecoviruses - Nature.com
articles.description: A computationally designed antigen based on the receptor binding domain of the spike protein of sarbecoviruses elicits broad humoral responses against severe acute respiratory syndrome viruses in mice, rabbits and guinea pigs.
